{"tid":1684701,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"香港第三季GDP按年跌2.9%　經濟正式陷技術性衰退","createTime":"2019-10-31T08:38:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T11:17:34.000Z","uid":246731,"like":157,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":87,"replies":[{"pid":"aadb1765b46b8842f6b59c78fbbe939deb15f257","tid":1684701,"uid":246731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T08:38:44.000Z","msg":"政府統計處公布本地生產總值預先估計數字，本港第三季經濟按年增長為2.9%，按季跌3.2%，是連續兩季錄得按季負增長，即本港已陷技術性衰退。香港上一次經濟衰退已是2009年初，當時GDP連續4季按季倒退。<br />\n<br />\n早前財政司司長陳茂波已於網誌撰文預告第三季經濟按季計會出現負增長，又形容香港「風急雨驟」，要達成政府全年經濟增長達0%至1%的預測，存在極大難度。特首林鄭月娥也稱，香港今年全年「好有機會」出現經濟負增長，事態非常嚴峻，會密切監察經濟下行情況，適時推出紓緩措施。<br />\n<br />\n投資銀行摩根士丹利報告則預估，今年下半年香港GDP將跌2%，是金融海嘯以來最低水平，全年計GDP或出現0.8%的倒退。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A/392850/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89%E5%AD%A3gdp%E6%8C%89%E5%B9%B4%E8%B7%8C2-9-%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E6%AD%A3%E5%BC%8F%E9%99%B7%E6%8A%80%E8%A1%93%E6%80%A7%E8%A1%B0%E9%80%80\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E7%25B6%2593%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E8%25A8%258A%2F392850%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%25AC%25AC%25E4%25B8%2589%25E5%25AD%25A3gdp%25E6%258C%2589%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%25B7%258C2-9-%25E7%25B6%2593%25E6%25BF%259F%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E5%25BC%258F%25E9%2599%25B7%25E6%258A%2580%25E8%25A1%2593%25E6%2580%25A7%25E8%25A1%25B0%25E9%2580%2580&d=N2LCmr%2FexNvWBpgyITFnA1GN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=3cea4258\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A/392850/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89%E5%AD%A3gdp%E6%8C%89%E5%B9%B4%E8%B7%8C2-9-%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E6%AD%A3%E5%BC%8F%E9%99%B7%E6%8A%80%E8%A1%93%E6%80%A7%E8%A1%B0%E9%80%80</a>"},{"pid":"3a0a9cd8f8be23e144f31826b50f4530be2b9195","tid":1684701,"uid":146030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T08:39:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=